### Authors and Contributors
My name is Mohammed Al-janabi, a PhD student at Keele university, Interested in Web scraping, Machine Learning and internet security. This GitHub page is for posting the practical part of my PhD research. The university web page here [using GitHub Flavored Markdown](http://www.scm.keele.ac.uk/staff/m_al-janabi/).
